cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "PRAG-AI: Chat with your research papers"
type: software
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: https://github.com/MINE-DD/PRAG-AI
abstract: >
  PRAG-AI is a local Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system that lets
  researchers ask questions across a collection of academic PDF papers and
  receive grounded, cited answers. Processing runs locally via Ollama,
  Qdrant, and Docling — papers never leave the user's machine.
